# Weather App

This is a weather application that allows users to check the current weather conditions for different locations using the Weather API by API Ninjas.

## Features

- **Current Weather:** Get real-time weather information including temperature, humidity, wind speed, and more for specific cities.
- **Search Functionality:** Enter the name of the city to fetch the weather details.
- **Responsive Design:** The app is designed to be responsive, ensuring a seamless experience across various devices.

## API Integration

This app uses the Weather API by API Ninjas to retrieve weather data. You will need to sign up on the [API Ninjas website](https://rapidapi.com/developer/account) to obtain an API key. Add your API key to the `index.js` file as shown below:

```javascript
const options = {
	method: 'GET',
	headers: {
		'X-RapidAPI-Key': 'YOUR_API_KEY_HERE',
		'X-RapidAPI-Host': 'weather-by-api-ninjas.p.rapidapi.com'
	}
};
